Class Tally

  • java.lang.Object
    • Tally

  • class Tally
extends java.lang.Object
    Class Inscriber retains methods which are used to create lists of objects like customers, items, order, quantities and display them. It also has methods to build charts with consumerId, itemId, orderId and barCode which are used to comparision with new values.
    Version:
    2.0 15.03.2018
    Author:
    Magdalena Wisniewska
    See Also:
    Item.setBarCode(), Order.setCustomerId(), Quantity.setItemId(), Quantity.setOrderId()
